                     <content styleCode="italics">Other Ingredients</content>
                  </content>
               </title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Glycerin, Sodium polyacrylate, Dihydroxyaluminum aminoacetate, Edetate disodium, Kaolin, Carboxymethylcellulose sodium, Titanium dioxide, L-Tartaric acid, Polyacrylic acid, Propylene glycol, Polysorbate 80, Isopropyl Myristate, Hydroxyacetophenone, Water, and PVP</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20220907"/>
            </section>
